The paper deals with dynamic ensemble selection techniques for classification tasks, which are commonly studied in the machine learning community. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision), which are also related to classification tasks. The paper also proposes a new method for selecting the region of competence, which involves selecting an equal number of samples from each class, which could be related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.DM (Data Mining).
